Module tagtraum.japlscript.executor
Package com.tagtraum.japlscript.execution

Class NativeLibraryLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tagtraum.japlscript.execution.NativeLibraryLoader

  • public final class NativeLibraryLoader
extends Object
    Loader for the native libraries. First tries to load a library the default way using System.loadLibrary(String), upon failure falls back to the base directory of the given class package or the jar the class is in. This way, a native library is found, if it is located in the same directory as a particular jar, identified by a specific class from that jar.
    Author:
    Hendrik Schreiber
